{"tid":2422833,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"食三哥嗌清湯比同學恥笑","createTime":"2021-02-25T13:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T13:50:04.000Z","uid":376170,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"33670bd0ca41be35861431f2392cadfafea2dd8f","tid":2422833,"uid":376170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"今個禮拜五就 last day<br />\n呢幾日就特登約多啲人一齊lunch<br />\n知道grad之後都冇咩機會咁多人一齊撚廚<br />\n<br />\n今日就約好咗食三哥<br />\n因為自己本身食唔到辣<br />\n所以嗌清湯<br />\n點知其中一個frd聽到就屌我話食譚仔嗌清湯不如咪撚食<br />\n其他frd又join埋一齊恥笑<br />\n搞到我好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想搵窿捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實夾硬食辣食唔曬咪又係嘥晒<br />\n食到辣你估我唔想食咩<br />\n就算有野飲<br />\n未食飽都已經飲飽啦<br />\n<br />\n利申屌我個個同學嗌十小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我嗌清湯都冇資格笑/屌番佢㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n清湯matter<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以陪樓主食清湯三哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0a73ca040cb98bb6e2dad3aeb92f326656ed07","tid":2422833,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"惺"},{"pid":"45f9832fed9b6b54230c2ec4e9e8f64af80dd6bd","tid":2422833,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"你琴日咪講左囉"},{"pid":"dad503883d766c7fef7e0a96fd066a84b90c2b8c","tid":2422833,"uid":376170,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"45f9832fed9b6b54230c2ec4e9e8f64af80dd6bd","tid":2422833,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"你琴日咪講左囉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.